  "texts": [
    "The average of all responses for Purpose and Expected Benefits are shown in brackets at the top of two respective columns.",
    "For example, in Table 5 Purpose was scored 3.63 i.e.",
    "91 % and Expected Benefits at 90%.",
    "The same pattern of scoring repeats in all other cases presented in Tables 5 to 14, with the lowest score (3.00 which is 75%) appearing in Table 11 which depicts the experts' responses on the Benefits of Appointing an Ombudsman.",
    "Reflecting on these responses as well as the criticisms we modified the McRE accordingly."
  ]
